 \det A_n=\begin{vmatrix}   2 & 1 & \cdots & 0 \\   1 & 2 & \cdots & 0 \\   \vdots  & \vdots  & \ddots & \vdots  \\   0 & 0 & \cdots & 2  \end{vmatrix}_{n\times n}=2\begin{vmatrix}   2 & 1 & \cdots & 0 \\   1 & 2 & \cdots & 0 \\   \vdots  & \vdots  & \ddots & \vdots  \\   0 & 0 & \cdots & 2  \end{vmatrix}_{n-1\times n-1}-1\begin{vmatrix}   1 & 0 & \cdots & 0 \\   0 & 2 & \cdots & 0 \\   \vdots  & \vdots  & \ddots & \vdots  \\   0 & 0 & \cdots & 2  \end{vmatrix}_{n-1\times n-1}\\ =2\det A_{n-1}-\det A_{n-2}. 
